text.tspan: Hi everyone! Is anyone else still trying to figure
out housing? I'm a little worried about rooming with other
law students, especially during my 1L year.
Hi Lucy! I can understand where
you're coming from. Rooming with another
stressed-out first year doesn't help. But you
should consider living with a 2L or 3L. They tend
to be a little more grounded and can offer some
much needed perspective about law school.
